{"id": "1493576678885298336", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "こんばんは。", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:40:29.559000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493576905725706439", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "昨日、フォローしていただいたおかげで、イベントの余韻第五幕までクリアできました。", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:41:23.642000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🎉", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "🍵", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
{"id": "1493577469578707024", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "薦められた高レベルサルバドルを借りました。", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:43:38.075000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493577921686798447", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "最初は勝手がわからなかったのですが、サルバドルの狂気解放で防御。祝福の骨肉で炉を貯めて、苦痛の解消で攻撃を繰り返すという方法をとっています。このやり方で良かったでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:45:25.866000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493578964160217188", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "content": "苦痛の解消の献身で炉をためて、苦痛の解消の浄化を連打して攻撃。苦痛の解消の救済で防御します", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:49:34.411000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493579117264769024", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "苦痛の解消だけで、事足りるんですか！？", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:50:10.914000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493579141046472805", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "content": "足りちゃいます", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:50:16.584000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493579519284744202", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "これ、他のステージでも大丈夫ですか？メヌエットだったかで、攻撃を無効化してくるのがいたのですが……", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:51:46.763000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493580591277408359", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "content": "よくわからんけど、サルバに勝てるステージは存在しないです", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:56:02.346000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "👈", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
{"id": "1493580663130034187", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "content": "ステージ側がチャレンジャーです", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:56:19.477000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493580939295461508", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "強いなー、おじいちゃん。", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:57:25.320000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493581016802136084", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "そして、たった今、サンガーさん3体目が来ました。", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:57:43.799000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493581052265107517", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "深海キャラが増えないなー", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:57:52.254000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493581463893839903", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "content": "特に拘りないなら超次元引くのオススメですよん", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T11:59:30.394000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493582593948651560", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "content": "サルバドルは､超次元入れると苦痛の解消を撃てる回数が増えてさらに強くなります😎", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T12:03:59.820000+00:00"}
{"id": "1493585091165945887", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "あー、その手があったか！", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T12:13:55.203000+00:00"}
